.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, grapefruit, nectarine, asparagus
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, reading, traveling
4 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, dog, goat
1. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
6. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | nectarine   | asparagus      | grapefruit       | plum |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | traveling | reading     | video-games |
| Pet     | goat     | lizard  | frog | dog |

