.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, coffee, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, romance, documentary, scientific
4 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, cat, bird
1. the owner of the cat is the person watching family movies##1
2. the owner of the turtle is between the person watching scientific movies and the owner of the lizard##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the person watching family movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water          | fanta | mirinda        |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | romance | scientific   | family     |
| Pet           | lizard | turtle         | bird         | cat |

