.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, woodworking, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, videographer, manager, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, rock, trance, indie
1. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
2. the manager is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the musician is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of rock is between the pilot and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the manager##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography | puzzles      | woodworking       | video-games    |
| Job           | videographer  | manager  | musician | pilot |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | trance | rock         | r&b    |

