.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, tea, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, lawyer, nurse, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cycling, rowing, climbing
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the bartender##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the bartender##3
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the bartender##1
7. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the lawyer is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
9. the musician is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk         | 7up  | tea     | almond-milk         |
| Job        | musician | lawyer | bartender | nurse         |
| Sport      | cycling         | rowing  | skateboarding   | climbing |

