.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, ambient, house
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, spanish, japanese
4 different pets are kept: frog, cat, hedgehog, pony
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
 2. the german is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 4. the spanish is between the fan of blues and the fan of hip-hop##2
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 6. the owner of the pony is the fan of ambient##1
 7. the japanese is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
 9. the polish is between the fan of house and the fan of ambient##2
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | ambient    | blues | house    |
| Nationality   | german | spanish | polish  | japanese |
| Pet           | hedgehog   | pony    | frog        | cat   |

