.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, musician, writer, police-officer
There are 4 different nationalities: british, nigerian, canadian, polish
1. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
2. the musician is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the polish is on the left or right of the writer##3
4. the musician is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
6. the polish is on the right of the musician##1
7. the nigerian is on the left of the musician##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
9. the person drinking water is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | water                | milk  | lemonade | cola   |
| Job           | police-officer | musician | entrepreneur   | writer |
| Nationality   | nigerian         | british     | polish     | canadian |

