.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, mirinda, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, spanish, brazilian, french
4 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, dog, ferret
1. the owner of the fish is between the person drinking mirinda and the canadian##2
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
7. the canadian is on the left or right of the french##3
8. the brazilian is the person drinking tea##1
9. the french is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | tea | mirinda      | lemonade  | milk    |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | spanish | french | canadian |
| Pet           | ferret      | dog       | fish   | lizard      |

