.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, puzzles, collecting, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, italian, polish, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo, soccer, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the argentine is between the person who's sport is skiing and the mexican##2
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
8. the italian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading    | collecting | puzzles  | board-games  |
| Nationality   | polish | italian       | argentine | mexican |
| Sport         | soccer   | skiing      | snowboarding | water-polo       |

