.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, sailing, handball, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, bus, boat, van
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the bus and the person who's sport is handball##2
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | sprite     | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk        |
| Sport       | handball   | cricket | sailing | basketball |
| Transport   | van | boat      | bus    | tram   |

