The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, horror, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, polish, chinese
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is between the indonesian and the person eating potato##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
4. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
5. the pakistani is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
7. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating potato is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | broccoli | potato  | cranberry   | spinach    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | horror     | thriller | mystery |
| Nationality   | polish   | chinese | pakistani | indonesian   |

