.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, garlic, raspberry, asparagus
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, gardening, magic-tricks
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, rabbit, goldfish
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
4. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
5. the person eating garlic is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | raspberry    | garlic    | kiwi  | asparagus |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | filmmaking | gardening      |
| Pet     | hedgehog   | fish        | goldfish   | rabbit       |

 